              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Reactor spectrum, approximates a Maxwellian",
                " distribution corresponding to a temperature of",
                " 350 K, for which the most probable neutron velocity",
                " is 2400 m/sec."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "1750 mg of melamine in a high-puritY graphite holder,",
                " which was inside an evacuated bismuth channel."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GE-IN",
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coaxial intrinsic germanium detector",
                " positioned inside a 20-cm diameter by 30-cm long",
                " NaI(Tl) annulus, operated either in the Compton-",
                " suppressed or pair-spectrometer mode.",
                "In the pair-spectrometer mode, the FWHM values are 2.3,",
                " 3.1, 3.8, and 4.5keV, respectively, for gamma-ray",
                " energies of 3, 5, 7, and 9 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
